You will need help with the Earth Staff (Doable by three groups of friends in your level range, or 1 strong group 60+)<br>
<br>
You will need 1 strong group in your level range for the Water Staff (Plan on 10 kills for the staff, feel lucky if you get it in less.) and you can do one good exp group to get the wand from Undertow in Kedge too. (At your level, Kedge has an awesome exp bonus so it’s worth it.... just grab those lonely Rangers and Druids that keep going<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong> /gu LFG!!!!</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> and tell them you have the BEST exp site.. they will thank you.. really.)<br>
<br>
You need one other Mage or Cleric friend your level for Slixin Kex and the Burning Woods Wurms.<br>
<br>
You need 1 strong group to get to the top of City of Mist and exp camp it until you get the torch.<br>
<br>
Farm 5-10k cash and buy the Pegasus Cloak MQ. (I posted on EQDruids and got 3 sales in 5 minutes heheh.)<br>
<br>
Don’t try to get your guild to Isle 7 unless they have a good number of people that need Sky items and it’s important on their agenda. Find a bridge, and schedule an all Mage raid. I can’t stress that enough.. it’s fantastic fun. (Crazy boring at times, but a blast when you are fighting and clearing.)<br>
<br>
You and 1 or 2 friends can kill Rottgrime easily.<br>
<br>
Other than that, you can do the rest yourself.<br>
<br>
All the drops will require some luck, so don’t drive yourself crazy timing spawns etc… just pass through a zone, whack the quest mobs and see if they have your piece. (The only real farming you will have to do is for the Power of the Orb mini quests… those suxxor, but at least you can farm fine steel in the process heheh.)<br>
